<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْحِكْمَة مِن مَشْرُوعِيَّة الدَّفْن<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{مِنْهَا خَلَقْنَاكُمْ، وَفِيهَا نُعِيدُكُمْ، وَمِنْهَا نُخْرِجُكُمْ تَارَةً أُخْرَى}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [طه/٥٥]</p> </div>